/* fonts */
export const FontFamily = {
  regular12: "Poppins_regular",
  semibold20: "Poppins_semibold",
  medium12: "Poppins_medium",
  headingH3: "Poppins_bold",
  plusJakartaSansSemibold: "Plus Jakarta Sans_semibold",
  skModernistRegular: "Sk-Modernist_regular",
  montserratSemibold: "Montserrat_semibold",
  nunitoSansRegular: "Nunito Sans_regular",
};
/* font sizes */
export const FontSize = {
  size_sm: 14,
  regular12_size: 12,
  size_3xl: 22,
  size_base: 16,
  size_21xl: 40,
  size_4xs: 9,
  size_lg: 18,
  size_5xs: 8,
  semibold20_size: 20,
  size_6xs: 7,
  size_3xs: 10,
  size_2xs: 11,
};
/* Colors */
export const Color = {
  pureWhite: "#fff",
  color2: "#e52479",
  purple: "#91228f",
  disabled: "#7b7a8c",
  grey: "#5e7389",
  slategray_100: "rgba(123, 122, 140, 0.64)",
  darkslategray_100: "#3d3d3d",
  darkslategray_200: "#1c3957",
  primaryColor: "#29256e",
  color1: "#191781",
  midnightblue_100: "#161659",
  secondaryColor: "#ef406a",
  snow: "#fefbfc",
  black: "#000",
  black: "#0d0d26",
  gray_100: "#090808",
  gray_200: "rgba(38, 38, 38, 0.56)",
  gray_300: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)",
  secondary300: "#90a3bf",
  bodyLight: "#8a9099",
  grey60: "#95969d",
  neutralDark: "#223263",
  bodyDark: "#595f69",
  royalblue: "#0079fb",
};
/* Paddings */
export const Padding = {
  p_xl: 20,
  p_3xs: 10,
};
/* border radiuses */
export const Border = {
  br_81xl: 100,
  br_15xl: 34,
  br_3xs: 10,
  br_8xs: 5,
  br_128xl: 147,
  br_17xl: 36,
  br_9xl: 28,
  br_9xs: 4,
  br_5xs: 8,
  br_7xs: 6,
  br_4xl: 23,
  br_base: 16,
  br_11xl: 30,
  br_2xl: 21,
  br_xs: 12,
  br_30xl: 49,
  br_11xs: 2,
  br_13xl_5: 33,
  br_8xl: 27,
};
